  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Digivolve] [Angemon]: Cost 3[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    If it''s your turn, search your security stack. This Digimon may digivolve into
    a Digimon card with the [Angel] or [Three Great Angels] trait among them with
    the digivolution cost reduced by 2. Then, shuffle your security stack. If this
    effect digivolved, you may place 1 Digimon card with the [Angel], [Archangel]
    or [Three Great Angels] trait from the hand at the bottom of your security stack.'
  InheritedEffectDiscription_JPN: "\u3010\u76F8\u624B\u306E\u30BF\u30FC\u30F3\u3011\u7279\u5FB4\u306B\u300C\u5929\u4F7F\u578B\u300D/\u300C\u5927\u5929\u4F7F\u578B\u300D/\u300C\u4E09\u5927\u5929\u4F7F\u300D\u3092\u6301\u3064\u81EA\u5206\u306E\u30C7\u30B8\u30E2\u30F3\u5168\u3066\u306F,\u226A\u30D6\u30ED\u30C3\u30AB\u30FC\u226B\u3092\u5F97\u308B\u3002\r"
